videos.description: Ehab Amin sends a pass down low to Francis Okoro, who pivots through two UCLA defenders and throws down the rim-rocking two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Okoro shakes off defense for two-handed jam) 2019/01/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Okoro shakes off defense for two-handed jam

videos.description: Paul White picks Jaylen Hands' pocket in the back-court, then Eurosteps around Alex Olesinski for the game-tying bucket and a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (White ties game with steal, and-1) 2019/01/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: White ties game with steal, and-1

videos.description: UCLA's Jaylen Hands collects the steal and slams it home, while Oregon Ehab Amin tries to get back on defense, but instead runs into the cameraman.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Amin runs into cameraman while trying to stop dunk) ESHEET 2019/1/10

videos.headline: Amin runs into cameraman while trying to stop dunk

videos.description: With 2.6 seconds left and UCLA down 2, Chris Smith ties the game but misses the free throw, sending the game to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB (UCLA ties game in final seconds, misses FT for win) 2019/1/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: UCLA ties game in final seconds, misses FT for win
